{"tid":1906172,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"(絲入)我想學下化妝","createTime":"2020-03-01T17:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T19:07:28.000Z","uid":323423,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"df245ef3ee7a6ca162d39f744b634c642c487f97","tid":1906172,"uid":323423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:52:02.000Z","msg":"我平時岀街都係素顏。依加十九歲，想汁下個樣先岀街<br />\n可唔可以講下化妝基本要用到d咩？我上網睇d片覺得佢哋用到好多嘢，唔太適合我，求指教"},{"pid":"7c0b6df72ccad0e377b40e0685a61494d280372b","tid":1906172,"uid":168730,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:54:37.000Z","msg":"好樣既唔洗化<br />\n醜既化都冇用"},{"pid":"45d857c62e82abcc1bf30a0d3461103bf77a999e","tid":1906172,"uid":237487,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"少粉底+ eye shadow ， 少mascara 算啦， 太多唔靚，小心越化越上引"},{"pid":"11f07d7103ed7afe298ae2d4017beb0ff5780654","tid":1906172,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45d857c62e82abcc1bf30a0d3461103bf77a999e","tid":1906172,"uid":237487,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"少粉底+ eye shadow ， 少mascara 算啦， 太多唔靚，小心越化越上引"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:58:04.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580cbff329f84316ed87c30f85fbe905d9e176ee","tid":1906172,"uid":262146,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:58:29.000Z","msg":"我初初嘗試化，用cc cream <br />\n之後用bb cream<br />\n之後再用底霜+粉底+唇膏<br />\n慢慢再化埋胭脂、眼影、眼線<br />\n一個全裝"},{"pid":"ea1743c5beb63981d716e0e01e1e1e1c82ee03c0","tid":1906172,"uid":204332,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"最基本修下眉畫眉<br />\n用遮瑕膏遮下黑眼圈/眼袋<br />\n搽少少唇膏，不過依家肺炎出去都戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n粉底blush嗰啲就睇下自己需要"},{"pid":"b213253847b240cbbc873df2f1abe5acfc693de9","tid":1906172,"uid":138634,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:59:36.000Z","msg":"戴con<br />\n保濕<br />\nBase<br />\n遮瑕<br />\n畫眉<br />\n鼻影<br />\n高光<br />\n眼線<br />\n眼影<br />\n睫毛膏<br />\n胭脂<br />\n唇膏<br />\n簡簡單單就呢啲 <br />\n慢慢學一樣一樣加上去<br />\n如果皮膚好就事半功倍"},{"pid":"85d43342fb433f328c97749db19c7812bd3805c2","tid":1906172,"uid":63426,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"理想：<br />\n<br />\n洗面<br />\n搽保濕<br />\n防曬<br />\n粉底<br />\n遮瑕<br />\n碎粉<br />\n畫眉<br />\n眼影<br />\n眼線<br />\n睫毛<br />\n胭脂<br />\n唇膏<br />\n光陰影<br />\n<br />\n現實：<br />\n保濕<br />\nCushion<br />\n鳩畫眉眼線<br />\n出門口先搽唇膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw宜家戴口罩唇膏都唔洗搽，不過照買新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113a2c03e79c53109071ad05a2e7a75343467007","tid":1906172,"uid":10623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T18:11:04.000Z","msg":"我未需要帶口罩時平時係<br />\n防曬 粉底 碎粉 眉粉 胭脂 陰影鼻影 唇膏<br />\n<br />\n我覺得咁樣出去已經成個人精神好多<br />\n所有嘢記得少量多次咁上<br />\n可以之後先慢慢學畫眼<br />\n平時睇多啲youtuber嗰啲新手入門片都好有幫助"},{"pid":"22778e1b379fd5c68cbf4995256a1d4caf2af180","tid":1906172,"uid":304200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T18:15:46.000Z","msg":"如果皮膚唔差 又剩係想化妝嘅<br />\n我覺得上粉餅 畫眉 mascara 胭脂 唇膏 已經好足夠<br />\n個人嚟講覺得胭脂好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搽咗望落精神同QQ好多"},{"pid":"473b0a96aaf3881cfcf0dbf618129b16658ce2e0","tid":1906172,"uid":323423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c0b6df72ccad0e377b40e0685a61494d280372b","tid":1906172,"uid":168730,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T17:54:37.000Z","msg":"好樣既唔洗化<br />\n醜既化都冇用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T18:21:59.000Z","msg":"自問唔算靚唔算醜"},{"pid":"df634bfcb46a9e692a8d7f823f3bc0c9edc7f61e","tid":1906172,"uid":323423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45d857c62e82abcc1bf30a0d3461103bf77a999e","tid":1906172,"uid":237487,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"202